loss正确的语义为0D Tensor，其shape为[]，当前使用了shape为[1]替代，也就是向量Tensor：

title: add sync bn and fix clip for npu
speed up yolo5
body:
1. Dataloader产生的Tensor都是pinned的，在训练过程中会出现多出同步H2D拷贝，造成打断。
  a. 这个模型的修复，只需将data["image"]转为gpu，别的可以先不用转
2. 前向随机位置出现gap，被Dataloader线程抢占GIL锁，导致主线程阻塞，无法加载Kernel 
  a. 原因是将use_shared_memory设为了false
3. ema运算不需要构建反向图，构建反向图是耗时的。可以加with no_grad
4. 有一段loss的运算在CPU上就可以，放到GPU上反而更慢
5. 本地实验，以上改动可以将IPS从60提升到100

title: Fix misalignment between SOT and dynamic mode
body:
`yolov5_loss`函数中SOT和动态图的行为没有对齐，导致SOT性能大幅度落后于动态图模式。

在`forward`函数中，还存在一处不对齐行为：
```python
if not self.to_static:
            tcls, tbox, indices, anch = self.build_targets(inputs, targets,
                                                           anchors)
else:
    tcls, tbox, indices, anch = self.build_targets_paddle(
        inputs, targets, anchors)
```
但是此处对执行性能无明显影响，暂不做出修改。

SOT模式下开启`use_shared_memory`执行会出错，暂未修复，详见`修复记录`.

目前开启`use_shared_memory`的情况下，动转静会报错，暂未修复。

title: Remove config update logic in benchmark script for dy2st mode
body: #108 在动转静下将 yaml 配置里的 `MosaicPerspective.mosaic_prob` 设置为了 `1.0`，而修改后动态图和动转静期是都是会挂在 dataloader 的，不修改的话动态图和动转静都不会挂，因此移除该修改，使动态图和动转静保持一致

title: update pre-commit config
body:
This pull request updates the `.pre-commit-config.yaml` file to replace and add pre-commit hooks, as well as update the versions of existing hooks. The most important changes include switching from `yapf` to `black` for Python formatting, adding the `ruff` hook, and updating the version of the `pre-commit-hooks` and `Lucas-C/pre-commit-hooks` repositories.

Updates to pre-commit hooks:

* Replaced the `yapf` hook with the `black` hook for Python formatting (`.pre-commit-config.yaml`).
* Added the `ruff` hook with the `--fix` argument (`.pre-commit-config.yaml`).

Version updates:

* Updated the `pre-commit-hooks` repository to version `v5.0.0` (`.pre-commit-config.yaml`).
* Updated the `Lucas-C/pre-commit-hooks` repository to version `v1.5.5` (`.pre-commit-config.yaml`).

title: 【Hackathon 8th No.37】Add YOLO11 for PaddleYOLO
body:
This pull request introduces the new YOLO11 architecture and its configurations. The changes include adding new configuration files, modifying existing initialization files to include YOLO11, and implementing the YOLO11 architecture along with its backbone and neck components.

### Introduction of YOLO11 Architecture:

* [`ppdet/modeling/architectures/yolo11.py`](diffhunk://#diff-1e551a20763a8110d7aa9f124e5ad04ac437b133cb2ae71d699e8d08e6f97df5R1-R114): Implemented the YOLO11 architecture, including the backbone, neck, and head components, as well as the forward pass and loss computation methods.

### Configuration Files:

* [`configs/yolo11/_base_/optimizer_100e.yml`](diffhunk://#diff-4290f5bcf2a3c74e46f442ccadffa8e6b59055a1902df07f3609e91274736527R1-R20): Added optimizer configuration with learning rate schedulers and optimizer settings for 100 epochs.
* [`configs/yolo11/_base_/optimizer_100e_high.yml`](diffhunk://#diff-e0c547d777f0a282e2bd130e86b089148c03108d1e5a9e8fa12459d3d459f650R1-R20): Added a high learning rate optimizer configuration for 100 epochs.
* [`configs/yolo11/_base_/yolo11_cspdarknet.yml`](diffhunk://#diff-5915cc499c990b19d692bb2dc1377b6baf084ef71958bb018a88e4944cbb8126R1-R35): Added base configuration for YOLO11 with CSPDarkNet backbone and YOLOv8 head.
* [`configs/yolo11/_base_/yolo11_reader.yml`](diffhunk://#diff-b1b6ca4cf1aa1dc6d7743a19fc076ecad50c21cc931f57e543f3356217d3f448R1-R45): Added data reader configuration for training, evaluation, and testing.
* [`configs/yolo11/_base_/yolo11_reader_high_aug.yml`](diffhunk://#diff-b01cf4fb2bcd63d2c414c67399996e307f7f420f25a708a29a5b2174737a4badR1-R45): Added data reader configuration with high augmentation for training, evaluation, and testing.
* [`configs/yolo11/yolo11_n_100e_coco.yml`](diffhunk://#diff-bad19303d15dcb41567b3bca8746233514b93cc0149ba7046c5318837bbc5bd2R1-R18): Added a complete configuration for training YOLO11 on the COCO dataset for 100 epochs.

### Modifications to Initialization Files:

* [`ppdet/modeling/architectures/__init__.py`](diffhunk://#diff-5584c74ce78706adb2479cd81d19e79574a658f1f134bebb73db24944d14aeffR27): Included YOLO11 in the architecture initialization file. [[1]](diffhunk://#diff-5584c74ce78706adb2479cd81d19e79574a658f1f134bebb73db24944d14aeffR27) [[2]](diffhunk://#diff-5584c74ce78706adb2479cd81d19e79574a658f1f134bebb73db24944d14aeffR41)
* [`ppdet/modeling/backbones/__init__.py`](diffhunk://#diff-6b7969c2721000d52037e737451b1cf021fa5dd66a540350c219aa9043e6cca1R32): Included YOLO11 CSPDarkNet in the backbone initialization file. [[1]](diffhunk://#diff-6b7969c2721000d52037e737451b1cf021fa5dd66a540350c219aa9043e6cca1R32) [[2]](diffhunk://#diff-6b7969c2721000d52037e737451b1cf021fa5dd66a540350c219aa9043e6cca1R51-R52)
* [`ppdet/modeling/necks/__init__.py`](diffhunk://#diff-f74050b89cbb2fef6ed2f42620ebecfda6e0de754af432ab5ed5174119a51800R24): Included YOLO11 PAFPN in the neck initialization file.
